</div><div class="page">
  <div class="page-header"><div class="page-header-title">Notre cabinet & notre démarche</div><div class="page-header-client">Pierre Dupont · 25 mai 2026</div></div>
  <div class="two-col">
    <div><div class="section"><div class="section-title">À propos</div><div class="info-block">
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Cabinet</span><span class="info-value">EcoPatrimoine Conseil</span></div>
      <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">ORIAS</span><span class="info-value">25006907</span></div>
