  <div class="section"><div class="section-title">Décomposition du calcul fiscal</div><div class="graph-box"><div class="graph-title">De vos revenus à l'impôt</div><svg width="490" height="190" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><text x="134" y="17" text-anchor="end" font-size="8" fill="#555" font-family="Lato,sans-serif">Revenus bruts</text>
