      <div class="section"><div class="section-title">Fiscalité patrimoniale</div><div class="graph-box">
        <div class="graph-title">Charge fiscale annuelle estimée</div>
        <svg width="240" height="64" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><text x="132" y="18" text-anchor="end" font-size="8" fill="#555" font-family="Lato,sans-serif">Impôt sur le revenu</text>
